# Titanic Data Cleaning & Visualization Project

## Objective
To clean, preprocess, and visualize the Titanic dataset using Python.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Google Colab

## Tasks Performed
- Handled missing values
- Removed duplicates
- Detected outliers
- Created visualizations

## Visualizations
- Survival Count
- Passenger Class Distribution
- Age Distribution
- Correlation Heatmap

## Outcome
Learned data preprocessing, visualization, and storytelling with data.
